nodes.text: Dalesham was a General of the Confederacy of Independent Systems. He was the commander of the local Separatist forces on Innton II. After the Nova Defiant crashed on the planet, he ordered the relocation of parts of the ship to the Great Cavern to be build into a base. The Clone Wars ended before the base could be completed and the Separatists abandoned it. Later the Rebel Alliance would come across the base, turning it into the Defiant Core.
